  "title": "Interior Designer #81685",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Interior Design</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Interior Designer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Kallang</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (Mon - Sat, 10.00am - 6.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Up to $3,600 per month + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Meet clients to understand their needs, preferences, budget, and timeline.</li><li>Prepare design proposals, mood boards, space planning layouts, and material/colour selections.</li><li>Produce design drawings and documentation (e.g., floor plans, elevations, 3D views) using relevant software.</li><li>Prepare quotations and presentation materials for client review.</li><li>Coordinate with suppliers and contractors on materials, site measurements, and installation details.</li><li>Conduct site visits to monitor progress, quality, and alignment with design intent.</li><li>Manage design changes and ensure proper documentation and communication to stakeholders.</li><li>Support project handover and address post-completion feedback where required.</li><li>Maintain clear records of design documents, client communications, and approvals.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Interior Design, Architecture, or a related field.</li><li>Prior experience in interior design (residential and/or commercial) is preferred.</li><li>Able to produce design drawings and basic 3D visuals.</li><li>Good communication and presentation skills to explain design concepts clearly.</li><li>Candidates without experience are welcome to apply, training will be provided</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81685 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
